{"tid":2296066,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：5千元津貼只適用於措施生效後「本地確診者」；明天起回家易開跑","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T09:10:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"baee4c25df516caf632758825a3e6af4a4fff819","tid":2296066,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"消息：5千元津貼只適用於措施生效後本地確診者<br />\n<br />\n政府將會為新型肺炎確診患者提供一筆過5000元津貼，細節待勞工及福利局敲定後公布。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，初步計劃是為接受檢測屬本地感染的確診者提供有關津貼，即經強制檢測後確診或特定檢測群組的人士，或自願檢測後的確診者，都可獲津貼，毋須作經資產審查，以避免繁複行政程序，不過津貼只適用於措施生效後的本地感染確診者。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始今早接受傳媒訪問時說，部分人尤其基層市民對強制檢測可能會卻步，擔心確診後會影響生計，因此當局會為確診者提供一筆過5000元津貼，勞福局定出細節後會盡快公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561307-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561307-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT5a4yQt1axGeSiCNDyOzEsA%3D&h=c05a67f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561307-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3b68cbe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561307-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"696205612ff23d48920cd70d7e1afc6d47b68926","tid":2296066,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"即係幾時開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1c48fbbe3446bc39b95b7b615905987ab915af","tid":2296066,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:52:35.000Z","msg":"快點傳染我"},{"pid":"1f1109268c32a227e9beb7bc33eaa343b16ca1c6","tid":2296066,"uid":52062,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:53:04.000Z","msg":"未開波,大家唔好偷步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ded0ee3212282f35c5c77348fa84039242c51e","tid":2296066,"